- Python 3.8+
- numpy >= 1.20.0
- pandas >= 1.3.0
- scipy >= 1.7.0

Optional:
- matplotlib >= 3.3.0 (for visualizations)
- seaborn >= 0.11.0 (for enhanced visualizations)

